Package: SCRuB
Type: Package
Title: Source-tracking for Contamination Removal in microBiomes
Version: 0.0.1
Author: George Austin, Liat Shenhav, Tal Korem
Maintainer: George Austin <gia2105@columbia.edu>
Description: SCRuB is an R package for capturing and removing a microbial dataset's background contamination using abundance observations among biological samples and negative controls. It provides functionlaities for:
    a) Estimating the most likely background contamination's relative abundance.
    b) Removing the background contamination from each inputted sample.
License: see file license.md
URL: https://github.com/korem-lab/SCRuB
BugReports: https://github.com/korem-lab/SCRuB/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
